2. If the browser MCP is unavailable or the navigation fails, tell the user: "Open `ONBOARDING.html` from your file explorer (double-click or drag to your browser). It's the visual guide to the full toolkit."

Then display:

---

**Welcome to PM OS!**

I've opened the **Onboarding Guide** in your browser — keep it around as a reference. It has the full toolkit overview, daily workflow, and every command you can use.

PM OS is an AI-powered workspace for Product Managers. You'll use it to generate documents (PRDs, One-Pagers, user stories), run daily rituals (morning briefing, reviews), track commitments, and stress-test decisions — all from right here.

